item.title: about codeVend
item.description: codeVend comes in for Software Developers who cant find the right platform to document and showcase their produts for their right prices. It comes with easy demo creation for the software uploaders and a critic board to test and debug your software. Your final year project could be the nect big thing, Electronic projects are not left out. by Manuel
